creator: Trainman #1 Indian Rail App
descriptionHtml:
Trainman app is the highest rated train app to book train ticket, check pnr status, train running status, live train status, seat availability & train enquiry. It is now available in 7 Indian languages namely Hindi, Marathi, Kannada, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali and Gujarati (अब पी. एन. आर. स्टेटस ट्रेनमेन एप्प 7 भारतीय भाषाओं में भी - हिंदी, मराठी, कन्नड़, तमिल, तेलुगु, बंगाली और गुजराती |)


Salient Features of this train app are listed below :-


Book Train Ticket

Trainman is now an IRCTC authorised online travel agent. Train tickets can be booked on Trainman in less than a minute. With secure payment, easy cancellations and fast refund, it is the most trusted app for train ticket booking.


Automagically read PNR number from IRCTC sms

The app automatically fetches PNR numbers from irctc pnr sms and saves it to my trip list. It also does pnr check in background from time to time and sends notification to user on any change. Train PNR status facility with pnr prediction for wait-listed tickets is also available.

Train between Stations & Seat Availability

Find train between station, train enquiry, check indian railway seat availability and get confirmation chances for waiting list tickets for general and tatkal quota. If seats are not available, this train app will suggest alternate trains to book confirm ticket. Check availability for 4 months in a view with seat availability calendar along with train fare for irctc.


Train Status, Offline Running Status & Train Enquiry

Check live train status to know if the train is running timely or late. Passengers when sitting inside train can also check train running status offline for which no internet & GPS is needed! This saves battery usage also. Know all trains arriving or departing at any station in next 4 hours with live station status. This feature is an extension to train running status in internet mode. Also check railway time table, historical platform number and average delay of any train at all its stops.


Train Timetable & Schedule

Know train schedule and route of train with halt duration at its stops. You can also check all the intermediate stations between any 2 stops while checking the live train status. This along with pnr enquiry prediction is one of the unique features of this train app.

Fare & Refund Calculator

Know fare for all the travel classes like first ac, second ac, third ac, sleeper, garib rath, chair car and second seating in a click. Also check fares for senior citizens, children and under other concessions. For rajdhani, shatabdi and duronto trains, check out the dynamic fare. Find out cancellation charges deducted depending on when the ticket is cancelled while doing pnr enquiry. This feature can be seen on train PNR status screen.


Platform number, coach position & seat map

Find out the platform number on which the train usually arrives. Also check the detailed coach composition of the train with rake reversal info. For any coach, passenger can check the seat layout plan.

Get food in train

Indian railway passenger can now book tasty and hygienic food from Trainman app and get it delivered at their seat while travelling. To get timely delivery of food, it is recommended that passenger should keep checking train running status and contact the customer care in case train is delayed at food delivery station.


Journey Card

24 hours before the train trip, a journey card is displayed at the top of home screen. This card does pnr check and displays latest pnr status at all times along with live train status.

Disclaimer

This app is privately managed and is not an official app by Indian Railway. It is not affiliated with CRIS or NTES. To check pnr status and train enquiry this app depends on other sources of information which might not be correct at all times.

Train between Stations & Seat Availability

Find train between station, train enquiry, check indian railway seat availability and get confirmation chances for waiting list tickets for general and tatkal quota. title: PNR Status, Train Running Status & Ticket Booking

creator: Trainman - Indian Rail App
descriptionHtml:
Train man app is the highest rated train app to book train ticket, check pnr status, train running status, live train status, seat availability & train enquiry. It is now available in 7 Indian languages namely Hindi, Marathi, Kannada, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali and Gujarati (अब पी. एन. आर. स्टेटस ट्रेनमेन एप्प 7 भारतीय भाषाओं में भी - हिंदी, मराठी, कन्नड़, तमिल, तेलुगु, बंगाली और गुजराती |)


Salient Features of this train app are listed below :-


Book Train Ticket

Train man is now an IRCTC authorised online travel agent. Train tickets can be booked on Train man in less than a minute. With secure payment, easy cancellations and fast refund, it is the most trusted app for train ticket booking.


Automagically read PNR number from IRCTC sms

The app automatically fetches PNR numbers from irctc pnr sms and saves it to my trip list. It also does pnr check in background from time to time and sends notification to user on any change. Train PNR status facility with pnr prediction for wait-listed tickets is also available.

Train between Stations & Seat Availability

Find train between station, train enquiry, check indian railway seat availability and get confirmation chances for waiting list tickets for general and tatkal quota. If seats are not available, this train app will suggest alternate trains to book confirm ticket. Check availability for 4 months in a view with seat availability calendar along with train fare for irctc.


Train Status, Offline Running Status & Train Enquiry

Check live train status to know if the train is running timely or late. Passengers when sitting inside train can also check train running status offline for which no internet & GPS is needed! This saves battery usage also. Know all trains arriving or departing at any station in next 4 hours with live station status. This feature is an extension to train running status in internet mode. Also check railway time table, historical platform number and average delay of any train at all its stops.


Train Timetable & Schedule

Know train schedule and route of train with halt duration at its stops. You can also check all the intermediate stations between any 2 stops while checking the live train status. This along with pnr enquiry prediction is one of the unique features of this train app.

Fare & Refund Calculator

Know fare for all the travel classes like first ac, second ac, third ac, sleeper, garib rath, chair car and second seating in a click. Also check fares for senior citizens, children and under other concessions. For rajdhani, shatabdi and duronto trains, check out the dynamic fare. Find out cancellation charges deducted depending on when the ticket is cancelled while doing pnr enquiry. This feature can be seen on train PNR status screen.


Platform number, coach position & seat map

Find out the platform number on which the train usually arrives. Also check the detailed coach composition of the train with rake reversal info. For any coach, passenger can check the seat layout plan.

Get food in train

Indian railway passenger can now book tasty and hygienic food from Train man app and get it delivered at their seat while travelling. To get timely delivery of food, it is recommended that passenger should keep checking train running status and contact the customer care in case train is delayed at food delivery station.


Journey Card

24 hours before the train trip, a journey card is displayed at the top of home screen. This card does pnr check and displays latest pnr status at all times along with live train status.

Disclaimer

This app is privately managed by Stark Enterprises Private Limited. It is not an official app by Indian Railway. It is not affiliated with CRIS or NTES. To check pnr status and train enquiry this app depends on other sources of information which might not be correct at all times.

Train Ticket Booking

Automagically read PNR number from IRCTC sms

The app automatically fetches PNR numbers from irctc pnr sms and saves it to my trip list. It also does pnr check in background from time to time and sends notification to user on any change. Train PNR status facility with pnr prediction for wait-listed tickets is also available.

Train between Stations & Seat Availability

Find train between station, train enquiry, check indian railway seat availability and get confirmation chances for waiting list tickets for general and tatkal quota. Train Timetable & Schedule

title: IRCTC Train Ticket Booking (Train man)

creator: Train man - IRCTC Authorised Partner
descriptionHtml:
Train man is the highest rated irctc app for train ticket booking used by over 1 crore train passengers. It is used to book confirm ticket, check pnr status, train running status, live train status, seat availability & train enquiry. It is now available in 7 Indian languages namely Hindi, Marathi, Kannada, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali and Gujarati (अब पी. एन. आर. स्टेटस ट्रेनमेन एप्प 7 भारतीय भाषाओं में भी - हिंदी, मराठी, कन्नड़, तमिल, तेलुगु, बंगाली और गुजराती |)


Salient Features of this train app are listed below :-


Train Ticket Booking

Train man ticket booking is now authorised by IRCTC. Confirm ticket for train can be booked on Train man in less than a minute. With secure payment, easy cancellations and fast refund, it is the most trusted app to book train ticket.


Automagically read PNR number from IRCTC sms

The app automatically fetches PNR numbers from irctc pnr sms and saves it to my trip list. It also does pnr check in background from time to time and sends notification to user on any change. Train PNR status facility with pnr prediction for wait-listed tickets is also available.

Train between Stations & Seat Availability

Find train between station, train enquiry, check indian railway seat availability before booking train ticket. Get confirmation chances for waiting list tickets for general and tatkal quota. If seats are not available, this train app will suggest alternate trains to book confirm ticket. Check availability for 4 months in a view with seat availability calendar along with train fare for irctc.


Train Status, Offline Running Status & Train Enquiry

Check live train status to know where is my train. Passengers when sitting inside train can also check train running status offline for which no internet & GPS is needed! This saves battery usage also. Know all trains arriving or departing at any station in next 4 hours with live station status. This feature is an extension to train running status in internet mode. Also check railway time table, historical platform number and average delay of any train at all its stops.


Train Timetable & Schedule

Know train schedule and route of train with halt duration at its stops. You can also check all the intermediate stations between any 2 stops while checking the live train status. This along with pnr enquiry prediction is one of the unique features of this train app.

Fare & Refund Calculator

Know fare for all the travel classes like first ac, second ac, third ac, sleeper, garib rath, chair car and second seating in a click. Also check fares for senior citizens, children and under other concessions. For rajdhani, shatabdi and duronto trains, check out the dynamic fare. Find out cancellation charges deducted depending on whether it is confirm ticket or RAC or waiting list. This feature can be seen on train PNR status screen.


Platform number, coach position & seat map

Find out the platform number on which the train usually arrives. Also check the detailed coach composition of the train with rake reversal info. For any coach, passenger can check the seat layout plan.

Journey Card

24 hours before the train trip, a journey card is displayed at the top of home screen. This card does pnr check and displays latest pnr status at all times along with live train status.

Disclaimer

This app is privately managed by Stark Enterprises Private Limited. It is not an official app by Indian Railway. It is not affiliated with CRIS, NTES, Ixigo, Railyatri or any other train app out there.

Happy Train Ticket Booking on Train man!

title: IRCTC Authorized Train Booking

creator: Train man - IRCTC Authorised Partner
descriptionHtml:
Train Man is the most popular app for booking train tickets with over 10 lakh users. It helps you check PNR status, train operating level, live train status, seat availability, & rail enquiry anywhere in India.

Booking a train ticket has never been easier. Seamlessly CLICK, SELECT, & BOOK a train ticket with our railway app available in seven languages: Hindi, Marathi, Kannada, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, & Gujarati.

Why choose us?
→IRCTC Authorised Partner🚆: Book your train ticket quickly & safely with 100 per cent safe payment options, simple cancellations, & fast refunds.

→Over 90% Accurate predictions✅: We value your money & your reservations. Know your possibilities of getting a ticket confirmation.

→Refund within 60 seconds💸: Have you changed your mind? Don't be concerned; we've got you covered. Your cancellations will be refunded immediately.

→Downloads & Reservations🎫: More than 80 lakh customers trusted Trainman to book their train tickets, & more than 15 lakh users did so. Don't put it off any longer; book your ticket immediately.

→Expert Customer support📱: Are you stuck? Don't worry. Our experts are right in front of you, ready to respond to your questions in a matter of minutes.

What we offer you
✓Coach layout⛸: For your convenience, a visual depiction on your phone. You have the option of selecting a window, middle, or aisle berth, depending on your preferences.

✓Train route🚆: To make the travel more educational while ensuring your safety. Plan your train route and check which station works best for you.

✓Seat availability💺: We appreciate your journey to provide you with a safe ride. The seats are available for your chosen train displays with special days, dates & seat numbers, as well as their pricing & percentage of availability.

✓Live station status 📈: To ensure that you do not miss your train, you can check the current position to see where it is & how long it will take to arrive at the desired platform.

Trainman App features
➢Train Timetables & Schedules 📆: Find out about the train schedule & route, as well as the length of each stop. You can also check any intermediate stations between any two stops while viewing the live train status. Together with the ability to predict PNR queries, it makes it remarkable.

➢Fares & Refunds Calculator 💰: Check out fares are for all travel classes, including first, second, & third class, sleeper, Garib rath, chair car, & second sitting for senior citizens, minors, & those who qualify for special reductions. Get dynamic fares for Rajdhani, Shatabdi, & Duronto trains & learn how much your charges will be if you cancel a confirmed ticket, a RAC ticket, or a ticket on the waiting list.

➢Cancelled/Diverted train 🗙: Your time & money are valuable to us. On the day, you can check your train has diverted or not from a specific stop, as well it is operating or cancelled.

➢Booking alarm⏰: If you have a date to travel before the booking for that date begins, you can set a booking alarm. It will remind you to book & make a successful journey on that date.

➢Order food 🍲: Choose your meal & payment method to deliver fantastic restaurant food to your train seat.

➢Book flights🛫: You may search & book premium economy, business, economy, & first-class flights.

➢Book hotel 🏨: You may book your preferred hotel through our most exemplary partner booking.com & get the best available discounts for your relaxing stay.

Usual typos: Mn Tran, Tranmn, Mn train, Trn mn

Disclaimer
Train Man is managed privately by Stark Enterprises Private Limited & is an IRCTC authorised partner. It is not an Indian Railways app. It is unrelated to CRIS, NTES, Ixigo, Railyatri, or any other train app.

We can help you book your dream trip tickets! Download the app now!

title: Train Man: Train Booking & PNR

creator: Train man - IRCTC Authorised Partner
descriptionHtml:
Trainman is a train ticket booking app with 5,000,000+ users. It instantly helps you book train tickets, check PNR status, live train status, seat availability & rail inquiry, anywhere in India.

Seamlessly CLICK, SELECT, & BOOK a ticket with our IRCTC train booking app in seven languages: Hindi, Marathi, Kannada, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, & Gujarati.

Why choose us?
→IRCTC Authorized Partner 🚆: Book your ticket on our IRCTC book ticket app quickly & safely with 100% safe payment options, simple cancellations & prompt refunds.

→Over 90% Accurate Predictions ✅: We value your money & reservations. Know your possibilities of getting a confirmed ticket on our IRCTC book ticket app.

→Refund Within 60 Seconds 💸: Have you changed your mind? Don't be concerned; we've got you covered. Your cancellations will be refunded immediately.

→Downloads & Reservations 🎫: More than 80 lakh customers trusted Trainman as their train ticket booking app, & more than 15 lakh users book train using our app. So, don't put it off any longer; book your confirmed train ticket immediately.

→Expert Customer Support📱: Are you stuck? Don't worry. Our experts are right in front of you, ready to respond to your questions in a matter of minutes.

What we offer you
✓Coach layout⛸: For your convenience, a visual depiction on your phone. On our IRCTC ticket booking app, you will get the option of selecting a window, middle, or aisle berth, depending on your preferences.

✓Train route🚆: To make your travel more informative while ensuring your safety, plan your train route and check which station works best for you on this IRCTC ticket booking platform.

✓Seat availability💺: We want to provide you with a safe ride. Seats are available for your chosen train displays with special days, dates & seat numbers, as well as their pricing & percentage of availability.

✓Live station status 📈: To ensure that you do not miss your train, you can check the current position to see where it is & how long it will take to arrive at the platform on this IRCTC train booking app.

Trainman App features
➢Train Timetables & Schedules 📆: Find out about the train schedule & route, as well as the length of each stop. You can also check any intermediate stations between any two stops while viewing the live train status. Together with the ability to predict PNR queries, it makes it remarkable.

➢Fares & Refunds Calculator 💰: This railway ticket booking app provides fares for all travel classes, including first, second, & third class, sleeper, Garib rath, chair car, & second sitting for senior citizens, minors, & those who qualify for special reductions. Get dynamic fares for Rajdhani, Shatabdi & Duronto trains. You can check the charges when you cancel a confirmed ticket, a RAC ticket, or a ticket on the waiting list.

➢Canceled/Diverted train 🗙: Your time & money are valuable to us. On the day, you can check if your train has diverted or not from a specific stop, as well it is operating or canceled.

➢Booking alarm⏰: If you have a date to travel before the booking for that date begins, you can set a booking alarm. It will remind you to book & make a successful journey on that date.

➢Order food 🍲: Our railway ticket booking app allows you to choose your meal & payment method to deliver delicious restaurant food to your train seat.

➢Book flights🛫: You may search & book premium economy, business, economy, & first-class flights.

➢Book hotel 🏨: You may book your preferred hotel through our most exemplary partner booking.com & get the best available discounts for your relaxing stay.

Usual typos: Mn Tran, Tranmn, Mn train, Trn mn

Disclaimer
Trainman is managed privately by Stark Enterprises Private Limited & is an IRCTC authorized partner. It is not an Indian Railways app. It is unrelated to CRIS, NTES, Ixigo, Railyatri, or any other train app.

We can help you book your dream trip tickets! Download the app now!

Trainman PNR Prediction

A one-stop app for all your book ticket and train booking, with the most thoughtful, clean, and user-friendly UI. Get your PNR Status Check, see where is my train, and check train coach position seamlessly- via the Trainman app.

Authorized Train Booking Partner.
You can assure your journey with Trip Assurance while you book Train ticket with Trainman.

Some Of Trainman, The App’s Features
  • Book Train Ticket
  • Trainman PNR Prediction
  • Trainman Train Ticket Booking
  • Free Flight with Trip Assurance
  • Get Confirm Train Ticket
  • Train Ticket Booking Is Safe And Secure
  • Train Booking & Enquiry Support

Book Train Ticket
  • Get the most accurate confirmation chances and Live PNR status prediction for Train Ticket Booking with Trainman.
  • You can check the status of your tatkal booking, and your 10-digit PNR number, which is printed on your ticket using the Trainman app. Get detailed analysis of coach position, live train status, train routes, train departure time, and train arrival time.
  • You can also use Trainman Live PNR Status to confirm tickets or see how likely you can book train tickets. Trainman is the best and highest rated Indian railway app for checking PNR status.

Trainman PNR Prediction
  • Get train reservation confirmation while you book train tickets and train running status to make your traveling decision seamless.
  • Prediction is computed using data analytics and machine learning techniques based on various factors such as previous booking and cancellation trends, station quotas, days of the week, seasonality, holidays, and so on.
  • Generally, tatkal booking live PNR Status has very few chances of being confirmed during peak festivals like Durga Puja (Dussehra), Diwali, and Holi, etc. But, with Trainman, you can book confirmed train tickets.

Trainman Train Ticket Booking
Confirm Ticket
With Trainman, you can book train tickets and increase your chances of getting confirmed train tickets. Use features like where is my train or coach positions are to make your travel seamless.

Free Flight with Trip Assurance
Book your ticket with us and by opting for our newly introduced “Trip Assurance” feature, you can avail Free Flight Ticket, if your train ticket remains waitlisted after chart preparation.

Free Train Ticket Cancellation
By using our Free Cancellation Feature, you can get a full refund on cancelled train ticket booking.

Train Ticket Booking Is Safe And Secure
Get an instant Refund upon cancellation of your online train ticket. Your ticket train booking is safe and secure with us.

Train Booking & Enquiry Support
Train Booking & Enquiry Support is available 24x7 for any train inquiry or questions.

Why Trainman Train Ticket Booking app?
Check Train schedules and seat availability easily in real time after for tatkal booking. Quick and secure train ticket booking solution. keep a tab on your train status Where is my train feature!

There are no credit card fees or hidden charges on the Trainman app when you pay using UPI or any source of payment. You'll get an in-app notification when your train ticket reservation is confirmed.

Get train arrival & departure time, train timetable, train time, coach position, and many other features only at trainman.
